  <md:title>The Second and Third Laws of Thermodynamics</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>State and explain the second and third laws of thermodynamics</item>
<item>Calculate entropy changes for phase transitions and chemical reactions under standard conditions</item>
</list></md:abstract>
